      <title>美国就业市场疫情缓解，衰退信号面临考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/us-job-market-s-pandemic-unwind-puts-recession-signals-to-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预测劳动力市场下滑从来都不是一件容易的事。但疫情后独特的形势让经济学家更难判断近期失业率的上升是否预示着未来会出现麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/us-job-market-s-pandemic-unwind-puts-recession-signals-to-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
